    <briefdescription>
<para>ChaCha20-Poly1305 AEAD — RFC 8439, pure C99. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides the Authenticated Encryption with Associated Data (AEAD) construction used by WireGuard for both handshake and transport encryption. Also exposes raw ChaCha20 for standalone use.</para>
<para>All state is caller-owned. No heap.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">uint8_t<sp/>key[32],<sp/>nonce[12],<sp/>tag[16];</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">uint8_t<sp/>plaintext[64],<sp/>ciphertext[64];</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Encrypt:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
